# Phone Bridge Project

## Project
Android-to-AI phone bridge. Outbound/inbound calls + SMS with AI voice at low latency.

## Stack
- Node.js / Python (TBD after research)
- VoiceBox (Docker) for TTS/STT
- Android bridge (ADB or app)
- Claude for AI conversation

## Rules
- Commit after every working milestone
- Keep latency as the #1 constraint for voice
- Document all Android bridge findings in /docs/research/
